title: Come Back Home
overview: In the beginning, successful stars were also aliens in Seoul who tried to fit in and struggled through hard times to become famous for a long time. Now, they return to the homes where they first started their lives in Seoul and meet the youth who are living in those homes to root for them. Korea's best host Yu Jae Seok, popular star Lee Young Ji, and humorous Lee Yong Jin visit various celebrities' first homes in Seoul.
